  "text": "Problems of type (MPOC) were considered from the viewpoint of disjunctive programming in [CITATION_1] , Section 7) first. In the latter paper, the author introduced reasonable stationarity notions and constraint qualifications for (MPOC). Let us fix a feasible pointx ∈ X of (MPOC). Frequently, we will make use of the index sets defined below:",
